Download TIGER shapes for Military Installations

Source: R/military.R
tt_military.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Military Installations

Usage

tt_military(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_military()
